name: algtrans_p0
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p0 (a b c d : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) ( hd : d > 0 ) : a^2 + (1/b)^2 + c^2 + d^2 ≥ a*(1/b) + (1/b)*c + c*d + d*a := by

name: algtrans_p1
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p1 (a b c : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) : (a^2)^4 + b^4 + c^4 ≥ ((a^2) + b + c) * (a^2) * b * c := by

name: algtrans_p2
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p2 (b c d : ℝ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) ( hd : d > 0 ) : ((Real.exp d) - 1)^4 + c^4 + d^4 ≥ (((Real.exp d) - 1) + c + d) * ((Real.exp d) - 1) * c * d := by

name: algtrans_p3
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p3 (a b c : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) : a^4 + ((Real.exp c) - 1)^4 + c^4 ≥ (a + ((Real.exp c) - 1) + c) * a * ((Real.exp c) - 1) * c := by

name: algtrans_p4
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p4 (a d e f : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hd : d > 0 ) ( he : e > 0 ) ( hf : f > 0 ) : d^2 + e^2 + f^2 + (a^2)^2 ≥ d*e + e*f + f*(a^2) + (a^2)*d := by

name: algtrans_p5
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p5 (a b c : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) : a^4 + (b^2)^4 + c^4 ≥ (a + (b^2) + c) * a * (b^2) * c := by

name: algtrans_p6
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p6 (a b c : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) : a^2 * b^2 + b^2 * (1/c)^2 + (1/c)^2 * a^2 ≥ (a + b + (1/c)) * a * b * (1/c) := by

name: algtrans_p7
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p7 (b c d : ℝ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) ( hd : d > 0 ) : ((Real.exp b) - 1)^2 * ((Real.exp c) - 1)^2 + ((Real.exp c) - 1)^2 * ((Real.exp d) - 1)^2 + ((Real.exp d) - 1)^2 * ((Real.exp b) - 1)^2 ≥ (((Real.exp b) - 1) + ((Real.exp c) - 1) + ((Real.exp d) - 1)) * ((Real.exp b) - 1) * ((Real.exp c) - 1) * ((Real.exp d) - 1) := by

name: algtrans_p8
formal_statement: theorem algtrans_p8 (a b c : ℝ) ( ha : a > 0 ) ( hb : b > 0 ) ( hc : c > 0 ) : (((Real.exp a) - 1) + ((Real.exp b) - 1) + ((Real.exp c) - 1))^3 ≥ 27 * ((Real.exp a) - 1) * ((Real.exp b) - 1) * ((Real.exp c) - 1) := by
